# Nova Multisig - Environment Variables Example
# Copy this file to .env and fill in your values

# ============================================
# ADMIN WALLET (REQUIRED for NVAI burn feature)
# ============================================
# This wallet pays multisig creation fees when users burn NVAI
# Format: Array of numbers (Solana keypair format) or base58 string
# IMPORTANT: This wallet is NOT added as a multisig member - users keep full control
# Example: ADMIN_KEY=[103,93,125,...]
ADMIN_KEY=

# ============================================
# RPC CONFIGURATION (Optional - has hardcoded default)
# ============================================
# Recommended: Use Helius, QuickNode, or Alchemy for production
# Free tiers available at:
# - Helius: https://www.helius.dev/ (100K req/day)
# - QuickNode: https://www.quicknode.com/ (20M credits/month)
# - Alchemy: https://www.alchemy.com/solana (300M compute units/month)
# 
# If not set, app uses hardcoded Helius endpoint in lib/utils.ts
# NEXT_PUBLIC_RPC_URL=https://mainnet.helius-rpc.com/?api-key=YOUR_KEY

# ============================================
# FIREBASE (Already configured in code)
# ============================================
# These are public and already in the codebase
# No need to set them here unless you want to override
# NEXT_PUBLIC_FIREBASE_API_KEY=AIzaSyCZsi5RaDwItGNf_KPee_2d9EsNJDtLsDI
# NEXT_PUBLIC_FIREBASE_PROJECT_ID=nova-a42e0

# ============================================
# IMPORTANT NOTES
# ============================================
# 1. Never commit .env files to git (already in .gitignore)
# 2. ADMIN_KEY must be kept secure (server-side only)
# 3. Fund admin wallet with ~1-5 SOL for multisig creations
# 4. NVAI token: 3SkFJRqMPTKZLqKK1MmY2mvAm711FGAtJ9ZbL6r1coin
# 5. Cost: ~0.01 SOL per multisig OR ~17,000 NVAI burn

